      "file_path": "catalog-be/src/main/java/org/openecomp/sdc/be/components/impl/ArtifactsBusinessLogic.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 4985,
      "message": "in case using wrapper pattern please use flat indentation.\nFor Example,\n\nCorrect Usage:\nif( errorWrapper.isEmpty() ){\n//Do Some Logic\n}\nif( errorWrapper.isEmpty() ){\n//Do Some Additional Logic\n}\nif( errorWrapper.isEmpty() ){\n//Do Even more Logic\n}\n\nIncorrect Usage:\nif( errorWrapper.isEmpty() ){\n//Do Some Logic\n}\nif( errorWrapper.isEmpty() ){\n//Do Some Additional Logic\n   if( errorWrapper.isEmpty() ){\n   //Do Even more Logic\n   }\n}",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2805,
        "name": "Michael Shitrit",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "ms172g@att.com",
        "username": "ms172g"
      },
